Diagram 1 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It's good for white to capture the black \'a1\'e3 stone without complaint.
\par
\par Black then extends with 2.
\par
\par This is similar to the original pattern but please try to remember that in this case black makes a small loss.
\par }
