Diagram 3 (Spiral Ladder)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par This is also an addional explanation.
\par
\par When black plays dansu with 1, if white captures with 2, white is in trouble.
\par
\par Black can drive white out with 3 and 5, creating a ladder. This type of ladder is called a spiral ladder.
\par
\par Be sure to watch out for it!
\par }
